Lead Scoring: Assigns scores to leads based on their demographics, behaviors, and interactions with your business. Lead scoring helps prioritize leads and identify the most qualified prospects.

Lead Nurturing: Enables automated lead nurturing campaigns through personalized emails, targeted content, and follow-up sequences. This helps move leads through the sales funnel and increases conversion rates.

Lead Assignment: Routes leads to the appropriate sales representatives or teams based on predefined criteria such as geography, industry, lead score, etc.

CRM Integration: Integrates with Customer Relationship Management (CRM) systems to ensure seamless communication and data synchronization between marketing and sales teams.

Reporting and Analytics: Provides insights into lead performance, conversion rates, sales pipeline metrics, and other key performance indicators (KPIs). This helps businesses optimize their lead generation and conversion strategies.

